Package ca.mcgill.splendorserver.model.userinventory

Class UserInventory

java.lang.Object
ca.mcgill.splendorserver.model.userinventory.UserInventory
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<Card>
public class UserInventory extends Object implements Iterable<Card>
Represents the inventory of a Splendor player. Contains cards and token piles. Observes CardView to assess whether a card is affordable. Observed by CardColumnView to add the card to the inventory. Observed by MoveManagerDepr to create the current move
